---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import LegalPage from "../components/LegalPage.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Notice | LONFRO">
  <LegalPage title="Cookie Notice" intro="Information about essential storage and future analytics configuration.">
    <h2>Essential storage</h2>
    <p>The website may store a small preference value in your browser to remember your cookie choice. This supports basic site operation and does not create a customer account.</p>
    <h2>Analytics tools</h2>
    <p>Locations for Google Analytics and TikTok Pixel are reserved for future launch configuration. No valid tracking IDs are included in this initial build.</p>
    <h2>Marketing measurement</h2>
    <p>If enabled, analytics may measure product views, WhatsApp clicks, inquiry-form starts and inquiry submissions. Configuration should follow the laws that apply to the final hosting and target markets.</p>
    <h2>Your choice</h2>
    <p>You can choose essential storage only or accept analytics in the website notice. You can also clear site data in your browser to reset the stored choice.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about website tracking can be sent to liangfen820817@gmail.com.</p>
  </LegalPage>
</BaseLayout>
